### professional  


# Headshots



### individual Headshots, Group portraits, & Branding sessions

Book Now

## How We Make Updating Your Headshot Easy:

  * We have a convenient studio location in Green Hills

  * We can travel to your location with studio lighting, backdrops, and a glam squad

  * We can match background, lighting, and sizing for your headshot requirements

  * Our average turnaround time is 2-3 business days for individual headshots, and 3-5 business days for large groups

  * We offer same-day delivery for individual headshots upon request for a $50 fee

  * Click here to learn more about our ERAS headshots for medical school and residency applications





### headshot packages



INDIVIDUALS GROUPS

Individual Headshots & Personal Branding Rates

$145 USD

EXPRESS INDIVIDUAL HEADSHOT

Indoor session (10 minutes); Grey, black or white backdrop; Digital delivery
of one edited image; Additional images and prints available for purchase.

$145 USD

$260 USD

BASIC INDIVIDUAL HEADSHOT

Indoor or outdoor session (30 minutes); Choice of backdrop; One wardrobe
change; Digital delivery of two edited images; Additional images and prints
available for purchase.

$260 USD

$560 USD

DELUXE PORTRAIT SESSION

Indoor and/or outdoor session (1 hour); Includes headshots and full-body
poses; Choice of backdrops or scenery; Multiple wardrobe changes; Digital
delivery of five edited images; Additional images and prints available for
purchase.

$560 USD

$850 USD

PERSONAL BRANDING SESSION

Indoor and/or outdoor session (1.5 hour); Includes headshots and full-body
poses, as well as a 90-second video highlighting your work; Choice of
backdrops or scenery; Multiple wardrobe changes; Digital delivery of 5 edited
images and one edited 90-second video clip; Additional images and prints
available for purchase.

$850 USD

Group Headshots & Portrait Rates

$135 USD

EXPRESS INDIVIDUAL HEADSHOTS

For 15 or more employees; Consecutive 5-minute sessions; Indoor or Outdoor;
One location; Choice of background; One edited image per person (PP).

$135 USD

$235 USD

BASIC INDIVIDUAL HEADSHOTS

For 15 or more employees; Consecutive 30-minute sessions; Indoor or Outdoor;
One location; Choice of background; Two edited images per person (PP).

$235 USD

$500 USD

GROUP PORTRAITS

For two or more employees in one image; Choice of backdrop; Digital delivery
of one retouched image included, additional digitals are 99 dollars per image.

$500 USD



For on-location photoshoots, we have a minimum purchase total of $1,000.
Travel fees may be applicable for locations more than 20 miles miles from our
office. Please contact us here to setup an onsite appointment.

Group discounts are available for groups of 15 or more (prices are listed
above). For large groups of 50 or more headshots, ask about our minimum
commitment discount where you can lock in a high-volume discounted rate per
person and save up to 50%. (Some purchases are subject to TN state sales tax,
9.25%)

Additional images from any session can be added to a package for a fee (see
pricing in studio).

BOOK NOW
